# @param {Integer[]} nums
# @param {String} s
# @param {Integer} d
# @return {Integer}
def sum_distance(nums, s, d)
  mod = 10**9 + 7
  movements = s.chars.map.with_index { |c, i| c == 'R' ? d : -d }
  updated_positions = nums.map.with_index { |num, i| num + movements[i] }
  distances = []

  updated_positions.combination(2) do |a, b|
    distances << (a - b).abs
  end

  distances.sum % mod
end
